Package org.bonitasoft.engine.business.application

Class AbstractApplicationUpdater<T extends AbstractApplicationUpdater<T>>

java.lang.Object
org.bonitasoft.engine.business.application.AbstractApplicationUpdater<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the concrete subtype of AbstractApplicationUpdater (for returning self, subclasses must ensure to use the concrete instance)
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
ApplicationLinkUpdater, ApplicationUpdater
@Deprecated(since="10.2.0") public abstract class AbstractApplicationUpdater<T extends AbstractApplicationUpdater<T>> extends Object implements Serializable
Deprecated.
This class should no longer be used. Since 9.0.0, Applications should be updated at startup.
Allows to define which IApplication fields will be updated
